        // After folding n elements the accumulator holds all 2^n subsets. The seed needs the List[List[Int]]
        // annotation (K0232) so the empty-list-of-lists type is known.
        //   [1,2,3] -> [[], [1], [2], [1,2], [3], [1,3], [2,3], [1,2,3]]  (2^3 = 8 subsets)
